com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Class DefaultManageWorkforceAvailabiltyService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.DefaultManageWorkforceAvailabiltyService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ManageWorkforceAvailabiltyService

    @Named
public class DefaultManageWorkforceAvailabiltyService
extends Object
implements ManageWorkforceAvailabiltyService

    This service enables you to add availability information to the S/4HANA system for customers that are not using SAP SuccessFactors Employee Central. The availability information includes the work schedule, the holiday information and the absence information of a person.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_MANAGE_WF_AVAILABILITY
    API Version:1
    Communication Scenario:External HR Workforce Integration (SAP_COM_0301)
    Scope Items:Employee Integration - SAP S/4HANA Enablement (1FD)
